<center>
<h1>New Account</h1>
</center>

アカウントを作成します.ユーザー名とパスワードを入力してください.

<div class="mx-auto" style="width: 300px;">
<form action="/newaccount" method="post">
<div class="form-group">
    <label for="exampleFormControlInput1">Username</label>
    <input type="text" class="form-control" name="uname" maxlength="40" placeholder="user">
  </div>
<div class="form-group">
    <label for="exampleFormControlInput1">Password</label>
    <input type="password" class="form-control" maxlength="40" name="pass1" >
  </div>
<div class="form-group">
    <label for="exampleFormControlInput1">Password Again</label>
    <input type="password" class="form-control" maxlength="40" name="pass2" >
  </div>
  <br>

<button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Create</button>
<button type="reset" class="btn btn-danger">Reset</button>
</form>
<a class="btn btn-link" data-toggle="collapse" href="/login" role="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseExample">
Login
</a>
<br>
<a class="btn btn-link" data-toggle="collapse" href="/forgetpass" role="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseExample">
Forget Password
</a>
</div>
